' @test valid
' @covers THINK, USING, TOOLS
' @description THINK with multiple tools available to LLM

TOOLS search, calculator

THINK analysis
  USING !search, !calculator
  GOAL <<
  Research the topic and calculate metrics.
  >>
  RESULT
  * findings: TEXT - research findings
  * metric: NUMBER - calculated metric
END

WAIT
  ON ?analysis
END

EXIT
